OL,5, The government has told the            
OL,6, organisation that reviews pay for      
OL,7, public sector workers, it is "vital" to
OL,8, take into account pay rises seen in    
OL,9, recent years, when setting wages.      
OL,11,FPay review bodies (PRBs) recommend the 
OL,12,Fpay for 2.5 million workers.           
OL,14,FPRBs consult the views of several      
OL,15,Fgroups including government            
OL,16,Fdepartments.                           
OL,18,FSome union leaders are concerned that  
OL,19,Fthe government's tone might mean pay   
OL,20,Fsettlements could be lower.            
